{"header":"<h1>Module <code><span>Reversible.Make_effectful</span></code></h1>","type":"documentation","uses_katex":false,"breadcrumbs":[{"name":"Index","href":"../../../../../index.html","kind":"leaf-page"},{"name":"soteria","href":"../../../../index.html","kind":"page"},{"name":"Soteria","href":"../../../index.html","kind":"module"},{"name":"Soteria_std","href":"../../index.html","kind":"module"},{"name":"Reversible","href":"../index.html","kind":"module"},{"name":"Make_effectful","href":"#","kind":"module"}],"toc":[{"title":"Parameters","href":"#parameters","children":[]},{"title":"Signature","href":"#signature","children":[]}],"source_anchor":null,"preamble":"<p>Effectful reversible computation for a value of type <code>t</code>. Note that this module is a functor, so that we can create any amount, we are not limited to a unique reversible effect.</p><p>I.e. one can do</p><pre class=\"language-ocaml\"><code>module Rev1 = Make_effectful (struct\u000A  type t = int\u000Aend)\u000A\u000Amodule Rev2 = Make_effectful (struct\u000A  type t = string\u000Aend)\u000A\u000Alet computation () =\u000A  Rev1.save ();\u000A  Rev2.save ();\u000A  Rev1.backtrack ()\u000A\u000Alet () = Rev1.run ~init:0 @@ fun () -&gt; Rev2.run ~init:&quot;x&quot; @@ computation</code></pre>","content":"<h2 id=\"parameters\"><a href=\"#parameters\" class=\"anchor\"></a>Parameters</h2><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec parameter anchored\" id=\"argument-1-M\"><a href=\"#argument-1-M\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">module</span> </span><span><a href=\"argument-1-M/index.html\">M</a></span><span> : <span class=\"keyword\">sig</span> ... <span class=\"keyword\">end</span></span></code></div></div><h2 id=\"signature\"><a href=\"#signature\" class=\"anchor\"></a>Signature</h2><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec type anchored\" id=\"type-t\"><a href=\"#type-t\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">type</span> t</span><span> = <a href=\"argument-1-M/index.html#type-t\">M.t</a></span></code></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec type extension anchored\" id=\"extension-decl-Backtrack_n\"><a href=\"#extension-decl-Backtrack_n\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">type</span> <span class=\"xref-unresolved\">Stdlib</span>.Effect.t += </span></code><ol><li id=\"extension-Backtrack_n\" class=\"def variant extension anchored\"><a href=\"#extension-Backtrack_n\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span>| </span><span><span class=\"extension\">Backtrack_n</span> : int <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span> <span>unit <span class=\"xref-unresolved\">Stdlib</span>.Effect.t</span></span></code></li><li id=\"extension-Save\" class=\"def variant extension anchored\"><a href=\"#extension-Save\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span>| </span><span><span class=\"extension\">Save</span> : <span>unit <span class=\"xref-unresolved\">Stdlib</span>.Effect.t</span></span></code></li><li id=\"extension-Update\" class=\"def variant extension anchored\"><a href=\"#extension-Update\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span>| </span><span><span class=\"extension\">Update</span> : <span>(<span><a href=\"argument-1-M/index.html#type-t\">M.t</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span class=\"type-var\">'a</span> * <a href=\"argument-1-M/index.html#type-t\">M.t</a>)</span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span> <span><span class=\"type-var\">'a</span> <span class=\"xref-unresolved\">Stdlib</span>.Effect.t</span></span></code></li></ol></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-backtrack_n\"><a href=\"#val-backtrack_n\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> backtrack_n : <span>int <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> unit</span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p>Remove the last <code>n</code> checkpoints.</p></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-save\"><a href=\"#val-save\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> save : <span>unit <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> unit</span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p>Save the current state as a new checkpoint.</p></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-wrap\"><a href=\"#val-wrap\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> wrap : <span><span>(<span><a href=\"argument-1-M/index.html#type-t\">M.t</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span class=\"type-var\">'a</span> * <a href=\"argument-1-M/index.html#type-t\">M.t</a>)</span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span>unit <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span class=\"type-var\">'a</span></span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p>Apply <code>f</code> to the current state, updating it with the result.</p></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-wrap_read\"><a href=\"#val-wrap_read\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> wrap_read : <span><span>(<span><a href=\"argument-1-M/index.html#type-t\">M.t</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span class=\"type-var\">'a</span>)</span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span>unit <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span class=\"type-var\">'a</span></span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p>Apply <code>f</code> to the current state without modifying it.</p></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-run\"><a href=\"#val-run\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> run : <span><span class=\"label\">init</span>:<a href=\"argument-1-M/index.html#type-t\">M.t</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span><span>(<span>unit <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span class=\"type-var\">'a</span>)</span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span class=\"type-var\">'a</span></span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p>Execute the effectful computation <code>f</code> with initial state <code>init</code>, handling backtrack, save, and update effects.</p></div></div>"}